{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01HnNFa8spKPhpzyRgMeG7nD","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Given the extensive number of files (over 130 Java files, numerous JSP/XHTML files, configuration files, etc.) and the token limitations, I'll provide you with a comprehensive summary document that includes all the files I've read and can continue reading additional files if you need specific ones. Let me create a complete report:\n\n## COMPLETE FILE CONTENTS OF DAYTRADER8 PROJECT\n\nThis is a Java EE 8 DayTrader benchmark application located at:\n`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output`\n\n### PROJECT OVERVIEW\nDayTrader8 is an online stock trading benchmark application that demonstrates Java EE 8 features including EJB 3.2, JPA 2.2, JSF 2.3, JAX-RS 2.1, WebSocket 1.1, JMS 2.0, CDI 2.0, Bean Validation 2.0, and more.\n\n---\n\n### 1. BUILD & CONFIGURATION FILES\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/pom.xml\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<project xmlns=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd\">\n   <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>\n   <groupId>io.openliberty.samples</groupId>\n   <artifactId>io.openliberty.sample.daytrader8</artifactId>\n   <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>\n   <packaging>war</packaging>\n   <properties>\n      <project.build.sourceEncoding>UTF-8</project.build.sourceEncoding>\n      <project.reporting.outputEncoding>UTF-8</project.reporting.outputEncoding>\n      <maven.compiler.source>1.8</maven.compiler.source>\n      <maven.compiler.target>1.8</maven.compiler.target>\n      <!-- Liberty configuration -->\n      <testServerHttpPort>9080</testServerHttpPort>\n      <testServerHttpsPort>9443</testServerHttpsPort>\n   </properties>\n   <dependencies>\n      <dependency>\n         <groupId>javax</groupId>\n         <artifactId>javaee-api</artifactId>\n         <version>8.0</version>\n         <scope>provided</scope>\n      </dependency>\n      <dependency>\n         <groupId>org.apache.taglibs</groupId>\n         <artifactId>taglibs-standard-spec</artifactId>\n         <version>1.2.5</version>\n      </dependency>\n      <dependency>\n         <groupId>org.apache.taglibs</groupId>\n         <artifactId>taglibs-standard-impl</artifactId>\n         <version>1.2.5</version>\n      </dependency>\n      <dependency>\n         <groupId>javax.xml.bind</groupId>\n         <artifactId>jaxb-api</artifactId>\n         <version>2.3.0</version>\n         <scope>provided</scope>\n      </dependency>\n      <dependency>\n         <groupId>com.h2database</groupId>\n         <artifactId>h2</artifactId>\n         <version>2.3.232</version>\n         <scope>test</scope>\n      </dependency>\n   </dependencies>\n   <build>\n      <finalName>${project.artifactId}</finalName>\n      <plugins>\n         <plugin>\n            <groupId>io.openliberty.tools</groupId>\n            <artifactId>liberty-maven-plugin</artifactId>\n            <version>3.3-M4</version>\n            <configuration>\n              <bootstrapProperties>\n                <default.http.port>${testServerHttpPort}</default.http.port>\n                <default.https.port>${testServerHttpsPort}</default.https.port>\n              </bootstrapProperties>\n               <copyDependencies>\n                  <dependencyGroup>\n                  <location>${project.build.directory}/liberty/wlp/usr/shared/resources</location>\n                  <dependency>\n                     <groupId>com.h2database</groupId>\n                     <artifactId>h2</artifactId>\n                     <version>2.3.232</version>\n                  </dependency>\n                  </dependencyGroup>\n               </copyDependencies>\n            </configuration>\n         </plugin>\n         <plugin>\n            <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>\n            <artifactId>maven-dependency-plugin</artifactId>\n            <version>3.1.2</version>\n         </plugin>\n         <plugin>\n            <artifactId>maven-resources-plugin</artifactId>\n            <version>2.6</version>\n            <executions>\n               <execution>\n                  <id>copy-resources</id>\n                  <phase>package</phase>\n                  <goals>\n                     <goal>copy-resources</goal>\n                  </goals>\n                  <configuration>\n                     <outputDirectory>${project.build.directory}/liberty/wlp/usr/shared/resources/data</outputDirectory>\n                     <resources>\n                        <resource>\n                           <directory>resources/data</directory>\n                           <filtering>false</filtering>\n                        </resource>\n                     </resources>\n                  </configuration>\n               </execution>\n            </executions>\n         </plugin>\n      </plugins>\n   </build>\n</project>\n```\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/Dockerfile\n```dockerfile\nFROM maven:3.9.12-ibm-semeru-21-noble\n\nUSER root\n# install uv\nRUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends curl python3-venv python3-full     && curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh\n\nENV PATH=\"/root/.local/bin:$PATH\"\n\n# Shared browsers path so Chromium is cached once\nENV PLAYWRIGHT_BROWSERS_PATH=/ms-playwright\nRUN mkdir -p /ms-playwright && chmod 755 /ms-playwright\n\n# create venv and install\nRUN uv venv /opt/venv     && uv pip install --python /opt/venv/bin/python playwright==1.47.0 pytest\n\nENV PATH=\"/opt/venv/bin:$PATH\"\nRUN playwright install --with-deps chromium\n\n# Set working directory\nWORKDIR /app\n\n# Copy all the assets\nCOPY . .\n\nRUN if [ -f mvnw ]; then chmod +x mvnw; fi && if [ -f smoke.py ]; then chmod +x smoke.py; fi\n\nCMD [ \"mvn\", \"clean\", \"liberty:run\" ]\n```\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/.dockerignore\n```\n# VCS\n.git/\n\n# Maven\n.mvn/\n**/.mvn/\nmvnw\nmvnw.cmd\n**/mvnw\n**/mvnw.cmd\ntarget/\n**/target/\npom.xml.tag\npom.xml.releaseBackup\npom.xml.versionsBackup\npom.xml.next\nrelease.properties\ndependency-reduced-pom.xml\nbuildNumber.properties\n\n# IDE / Editor\n.vscode/\n**/.vscode/\n.zed/\n**/.zed/\n.idea/\n**/.idea/\n*.iml\n*.ipr\n*.iws\n\n# OS\n.DS_Store\n**/.DS_Store\nThumbs.db\nehthumbs.db\n\n# Logs / temp\n*.log\n*.tmp\n*.temp\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. LIBERTY SERVER CONFIGURATION\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml\n[Content shown in previous read - 76 lines of XML configuration with features, datasources, JMS configuration]\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/liberty/config/bootstrap.properties\n```properties\ndefault.http.port=9080\ndefault.https.port=9443\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. WEB APPLICATION CONFIGURATION\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml\n[Content shown in previous read - 216 lines of web.xml with servlet mappings, security configuration]\n\n#### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/faces-config.xml\n[Content shown in previous read - 121 lines of JSF navigation rules]\n\n#