{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012cytam7rdytdbG3QvQJjiy","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully fixed all the Java files in the DayTrader Spring Boot migration. Here's a summary of what was corrected:\n\n## Summary of Fixed Files\n\n### 1. **TradeAppServlet.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeAppServlet.java)\n- Removed `import jakarta.servlet.http.PushBuilder` (removed in Servlet 6.0)\n- Removed `import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces.Trace` (deleted interface)\n- Removed `@Trace` annotation\n- Changed `@Inject` to `@Autowired` from Spring\n- Fixed `javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest` to `HttpServletRequest`\n- Fixed `javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse` to `HttpServletResponse`\n- Removed `pushHeaderImages` method and its call\n\n### 2. **TradeServletAction.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeServletAction.java)\n- Fixed all `javax.servlet.ServletException` to `ServletException`\n- Fixed `javax.ejb.FinderException` to generic `Exception`\n- Updated Javadoc comments from `@exception javax.servlet.ServletException` to `@exception jakarta.servlet.ServletException`\n\n### 3. **TradeScenarioServlet.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeScenarioServlet.java)\n- Fixed `javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest` to `HttpServletRequest`\n- Fixed `javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse` to `HttpServletResponse`\n\n### 4. **TradeWebContextListener.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeWebContextListener.java)\n- Deleted `import static javax.faces.annotation.FacesConfig.Version.JSF_2_3` (JSF removed)\n- Removed any `@FacesConfig` annotation\n\n### 5. **TradeConfigServlet.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeConfigServlet.java)\n- Removed `import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.impl.direct.TradeDirectDBUtils` (deleted class)\n- Removed `import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces.Trace` (deleted interface)\n- Removed `@Trace` annotation\n- Removed `@Inject private TradeDirectDBUtils dbUtils` field\n- Removed `doResetTrade` and `buildDB` action handlers\n- Kept only config display/update functionality\n\n### 6. **OrdersAlertFilter.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/OrdersAlertFilter.java)\n- Removed CDI imports (`jakarta.enterprise.inject.Any`, `jakarta.enterprise.inject.Instance`)\n- Removed `import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces.Trace` (deleted)\n- Removed `import com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.TradeRunTimeModeLiteral` (deleted)\n- Removed `@Trace` annotation\n- Replaced CDI Instance constructor with `@Autowired private TradeServices tradeAction` field injection\n- Added default constructor\n\n### 7. **TestServlet.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TestServlet.java)\n- Removed CDI imports (`jakarta.enterprise.inject.Any`, `jakarta.enterprise.inject.Instance